These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Job: engineer, security-guard, social-worker, accountant
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Job:social-worker##1
2. Job:accountant is on the far left##1
3. Job:social-worker is between Job:security-guard and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Job      | accountant | engineer | social-worker   | security-guard |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Cigar: bluemaster, swisher, fonseca, davidoff
1. Cigar:davidoff is between Hobby:reading and Cigar:swisher##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Cigar:fonseca is on the right of Cigar:bluemaster##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Cigar:bluemaster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Cigar   | swisher    | davidoff   | bluemaster | fonseca       |

