.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Music-Genre: indie, gospel, disco, trance
Nationality: australian, british, colombian, french
1. Nationality:colombian is on the right of Music-Genre:trance##1
2. Nationality:colombian is between Nationality:british and Music-Genre:gospel##2
3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Music-Genre:disco##1
5. Music-Genre:gospel == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | trance    | indie | gospel   | disco  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

